Title: Cyberostracism and the Needs Threat Scale
Description: This study seeks to investigate how cyberostracism impacts Williams' Needs Threat Scale (belongingness, self-esteem, meaningful existence, and control). Additionally, the study explores how ostracism source importance affects those four needs differentially
Contributors: Kathryn P Coddington, Lane Vanderford, Jon Grahe
Tags: cyberostracism, belongingness, self-esteem, meaningful existence, control, ostracism, needs threat scale, source importance

Cyberostracism and the Needs Threat Scale
This study seeks to investigate how cyberostracism impacts Williams' Needs Threat Scale (belongingness, self-esteem, meaningful existence, and control). Additionally, the study explores how ostracism source importance affects those four needs differentially
